%% Data Science Pipelines - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant API as ml-pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant Pod as Pipeline Pod<br/>(driver + launcher)
    participant MLMD as metadata-grpc<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant S3 as Object Storage<br/>9000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant DB as Database<br/>3306/5432 TCP
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant SWF as Scheduled Workflow<br/>Controller
    participant Cache as cache-server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Execution

    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>Auth: Kubeflow UserID Header
    API->>DB: Store run metadata<br/>MySQL/PostgreSQL protocol
    API->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8s->>Argo: Watch: new Workflow
    Argo->>K8s: Create pipeline step Pods<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token

    Note over K8s,Cache: Flow 4: Step Caching Check
    K8s->>Cache: Pod admission webhook<br/>HTTPS/TLS, K8s API cert
    Cache->>DB: Check cache hit<br/>DB protocol
    DB-->>Cache: Cache result
    Cache-->>K8s: Mutate pod (skip if cached)

    K8s-->>Pod: Pod scheduled & started
    Pod->>MLMD: Record execution start<br/>gRPC plaintext
    Pod->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>Auth: Access Key/Secret Key
    S3-->>Pod: Artifact data
    Note over Pod: Execute user container
    Pod->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>Auth: Access Key/Secret Key
    Pod->>MLMD: Record artifacts & lineage<br/>gRPC plaintext

    Note over PA,API: Status Reporting
    PA->>K8s: Watch Workflow status<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>PA: Workflow status update
    PA->>API: Report run status<br/>gRPC, Projected SA Token (1h)

    Note over User,SWF: Flow 3: Scheduled/Recurring Run

    User->>API: POST /apis/v2beta1/recurringruns<br/>Auth: Kubeflow UserID Header
    API->>K8s: Create ScheduledWorkflow CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    SWF->>K8s: Watch ScheduledWorkflow CRs<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Note over SWF: Cron trigger fires
    SWF->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Note over K8s,Pod: Pipeline executes (Flow 1, steps 4-8)

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Artifact/Metadata Browsing

    participant UI as ml-pipeline-ui<br/>3000/TCP HTTP
    participant Envoy as metadata-envoy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC-Web

    User->>UI: Browse pipeline results
    UI->>API: GET /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>Kubeflow UserID Header
    API-->>UI: Run details
    UI->>Envoy: Fetch artifact metadata<br/>HTTP gRPC-Web
    Envoy->>MLMD: gRPC request
    MLMD-->>Envoy: Artifact metadata
    Envoy-->>UI: Metadata response
    UI->>S3: Fetch artifact content<br/>Auth: Access Key/Secret Key
    S3-->>UI: Artifact data
